00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:54,520
Look.

497
00:21:56,310 --> 00:21:57,800
He even hit me.

498
00:22:00,430 --> 00:22:02,230
He is old

499
00:22:02,590 --> 00:22:04,470
and gets confused inevitably.

500
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,400
I wish him

501
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:08,830
not to do anything wrong to the country.

502
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:12,470
What do you want then?

503
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:16,310
Mr. Liu. I hope you can

504
00:22:17,430 --> 00:22:19,000
persuade him to hand over

505
00:22:19,950 --> 00:22:20,760
his military power to me

506
00:22:22,110 --> 00:22:23,040
and let me lead army

507
00:22:23,560 --> 00:22:24,470
to the battlefield.

508
00:22:30,560 --> 00:22:32,110
Mr. Cao, you’re determined

509
00:22:33,520 --> 00:22:35,280
to serve the Party and the nation.

510
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:37,400
That’s admirable.

511
00:22:38,710 --> 00:22:40,710
I’ll certainly consider your proposal.

512
00:22:41,710 --> 00:22:43,400
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

513
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:46,190
Enjoy the show.

514
00:22:46,830 --> 00:22:47,590
Goodbye.

515
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:49,070
Goodbye.

516
00:23:00,710 --> 00:23:07,520
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

517
00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:09,310
-Excellent performer!
-Excellent performer!

518
00:23:09,310 --> 00:23:14,830
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

519
00:23:14,830 --> 00:23:15,800
Excellent musician!

520
00:23:15,950 --> 00:23:17,310
Mr. Shang

521
00:23:17,310 --> 00:23:18,470
did a great job today.

522
00:23:18,950 --> 00:23:19,470
I think

523
00:23:19,830 --> 00:23:22,310
he’ll be the leader of opera association for sure.

524
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:25,400
Cheng. Your investment is worthy.

525
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:26,640
Excellent musician!

526
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:34,470
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

527
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:36,920
Zhouzi. Your performance was amazing.

528
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:38,040
I’ll help you in a while.

529
00:23:41,430 --> 00:23:43,350
His appearance in costume was great today.

530
00:23:43,350 --> 00:23:44,040
Right?

531
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:45,710
His makeup was good as well.

532
00:23:46,040 --> 00:23:47,310
I don’t even want to remove it for him.

533
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:48,280
Then keep it.

534
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:56,800
What’s going on?

535
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,430
What are they doing here?

536
00:24:01,430 --> 00:24:02,350
I don’t know.

537
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:04,520
Why are they here?

538
00:24:04,710 --> 00:24:05,400
Right.

539
00:24:10,110 --> 00:24:12,560
You performed so well.

540
00:24:23,040 --> 00:24:24,880
The appearance was handsome, too.

541
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:32,560
Don’t move. Behave.

542
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:34,000
Leader! Leader...

543
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:36,760
Mr. Zhou.

544
00:24:37,070 --> 00:24:39,710
I can’t afford to be your leader.

545
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:41,920
Isn’t Shang Xirui your leader?

546
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:44,520
I didn’t feel it right.

547
00:24:45,520 --> 00:24:46,710
How could the Spring and Autumn Love

548
00:24:46,710 --> 00:24:48,830
be so weird that day?

549
00:24:49,710 --> 00:24:50,680
I see.

550
00:24:51,230 --> 00:24:53,430
You’ve long hooked up with him.

551
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:55,640
Bite the hand that feeds you.

552
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:57,040
I’ll tear you apart.

553
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:58,310
Mr. Shang! Help! Help...

554
00:24:59,230 --> 00:24:59,470
Don’t move.

555
00:24:59,470 --> 00:25:00,400
Mr. Shang.

556
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:03,800
Who are you calling for help?

557
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:05,640
Who can help you?

558
00:25:06,070 --> 00:25:07,800
I still have your title deed.

559
00:25:08,710 --> 00:25:10,880
You'll never leave Yunxi Theater.

560
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:11,950
Help!

561
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:13,470
Help! Help!

562
00:25:13,470 --> 00:25:14,430
What are you doing?

563
00:25:15,070 --> 00:25:16,040
What’s happening?

564
00:25:16,230 --> 00:25:16,800
Let go!

565
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:17,950
-Don't move!
-Who are you?

566
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:20,350
How dare you make a scene in Shuiyun Theater?

567
00:25:20,350 --> 00:25:22,040
Stand right there! Don’t you dare!

568
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:22,920
Don’t move.

569
00:25:28,140 --> 00:25:29,140
What are you doing?

570
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:30,330
Hey!

571
00:25:30,330 --> 00:25:31,920
When I debuted and went popular.

572
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:32,590
Let go.

573
00:25:33,110 --> 00:25:35,310
You’re still in your mother’s belly.

574
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:36,560
You shrew.

575
00:25:36,760 --> 00:25:38,350
How dare you argue with me?

576
00:25:38,350 --> 00:25:39,190
What are you talking about?

577
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:40,710
You hit her?

578
00:25:40,710 --> 00:25:43,160
Shuiyun Theater is capable, huh?

579
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:48,000
You tricked my apprentice here

580
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,560
and performed for you?

581
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:52,880
What?

582
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:57,190
It’s Shang Xirui’s dirty trick, isn’t it?

583
00:25:58,040 --> 00:25:59,520
Call him here!

584
00:25:59,710 --> 00:26:02,230
Old man, how dare you call our leader?

585
00:26:02,230 --> 00:26:02,880
Beat him up!

586
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:04,230
Hit!

587
00:26:04,230 --> 00:26:05,190
What are you doing?

588
00:26:05,470 --> 00:26:07,000
You traitor!

589
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:07,880
Let go!

590
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,760
You ungrateful bastard!

591
00:26:11,760 --> 00:26:12,470
What are you doing?

592
00:26:12,560 --> 00:26:13,760
-Let go!
-Stop it!

593
00:26:14,520 --> 00:26:16,280
Enough! Stop!

594
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:17,230
What are you doing?

595
00:26:17,230 --> 00:26:18,680
Let go! Let go!

596
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:21,400
-Stop!
-Let go!

597
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,350
Let him go! Let go!

598
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:24,230
Let go!

599
00:26:24,830 --> 00:26:26,000
I said stop it. Didn’t you hear me?

600
00:26:26,230 --> 00:26:27,880
I’m not your man.

601
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:30,310
Why should I listen to you?

602
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:33,920
You meddle with our theater’s business?

603
00:26:36,230 --> 00:26:37,920
You played the emperor on stage.

604
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:40,070
You really take yourself as a true emperor?

605
00:26:42,710 --> 00:26:43,950
We had a deal

606
00:26:43,950 --> 00:26:44,830
of one month. Right?

607
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:47,230
You have the nerve to bring it up?

608
00:26:50,190 --> 00:26:52,160
I was too careless

609
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:54,110
and fooled by you.

610
00:26:54,830 --> 00:26:56,920
Who was that stranger Mrs. Wang?

611
00:26:57,350 --> 00:26:59,070
Was she a shill sent by you?

612
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:01,430
You played the dirty trick

613
00:27:01,430 --> 00:27:02,760
to get my man.

614
00:27:03,070 --> 00:27:05,310
You’re going to be struck by lightning.

615
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:06,710
That’s our grudge.

616
00:27:06,710 --> 00:27:07,830
Why did you hit him?

617
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,190
Hit me if you want.

618
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:10,230
Fine.

619
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:13,070
You asked me to do this.

620
00:27:15,470 --> 00:27:16,400
What are you doing?

621
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,230
How dare I hit you?

622
00:27:24,430 --> 00:27:26,920
You have someone powerful support you.

623
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:30,350
But he

624
00:27:31,070 --> 00:27:33,590
won’t get it over easily.

625
00:27:35,230 --> 00:27:36,160
Zhouzi.

626
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:39,190
Do you want to return to Yunxi or stay in Shuiyun?

627
00:27:39,760 --> 00:27:40,800
Zhouzi.

628
00:27:43,280 --> 00:27:44,280
If you want to stay here,

629
00:27:44,950 --> 00:27:45,880
say it loudly.

630
00:27:46,470 --> 00:27:46,760
Say it.

631
00:27:46,760 --> 00:27:48,070
I want to stay in Shuiyun!

632
00:27:48,310 --> 00:27:48,830
You...

633
00:27:50,230 --> 00:27:51,040
-Fine.
-What are you doing?

634
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:51,680
Sixi’er.

635
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,040
Don’t force him!

636
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:56,070
I will pay you tenfold money of the title deed.

637
00:27:56,230 --> 00:27:57,190
From today on,

638
00:27:57,400 --> 00:27:59,470
Zhouzi is Shuiyun’s performer.

639
00:28:00,800 --> 00:28:01,800
Tenfold?

640
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:04,800
Yes. Not one cent less.

641
00:28:07,710 --> 00:28:08,280
Tenfold?

642
00:28:17,590 --> 00:28:18,710
Buh.

643
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:21,310
In your dream.

644
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:24,160
I just want him to die,

645
00:28:24,710 --> 00:28:26,470
no matter how much money you pay.

646
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,160
Leader! Leader!

647
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,830
Mr. Shang! Mr. Shang!

648
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:31,760
Mr. Shang!

649
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:32,880
-Leader!
-Leader!

650
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,800
-Zhouzi.
-Zhouzi.

651
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:38,430
-Zhouzi.
-Zhouzi.

652
00:28:38,430 --> 00:28:41,000
Leader! Leader!

653
00:28:43,040 --> 00:28:43,590
Zhouzi.

654
00:28:43,590 --> 00:28:44,280
He still has breath.

655
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:45,350
Take him to hospital.

656
00:28:45,350 --> 00:28:46,110
Hurry. Hurry.

657
00:28:46,110 --> 00:28:47,640
You see?

658
00:28:48,230 --> 00:28:50,430
Hadn’t Shuiyun Theater forced him,

659
00:28:50,430 --> 00:28:51,760
how could he hit the wall?

660
00:28:51,760 --> 00:28:52,190
You...

661
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:54,110
Don't take him to hospital.

662
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:55,950
Come and take him back.

663
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:59,110
Whether alive or dead, that’s his fate.

664
00:28:59,430 --> 00:29:00,680
-Yes.
-Yes.

665
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:06,190
-Leader.
-Leader.

666
00:29:06,190 --> 00:29:07,400
Zhouzi...

667
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:09,310
-Leader!
-Leader!

668
00:29:09,470 --> 00:29:10,590
Mr. Shang.

669
00:29:11,280 --> 00:29:13,040
The title deed is still in my hands.

670
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:16,040
Alive, he is Yunxi’s performer.

671
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:19,920
Dead, he is still our corpse.

672
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:29,640
Mother.

673
00:29:30,190 --> 00:29:30,560
This...

674
00:29:46,060 --> 00:29:55,060
(Condolence)

675
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:37,470
Did Fujin go peacefully?

676
00:30:39,710 --> 00:30:41,350
She passed away in her dream,

677
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:43,830
without suffering

678
00:30:44,190 --> 00:30:45,470
from pain.

679
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:49,040
Fujin was blessed.

680
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:50,590
Pull yourself together.

681
00:30:55,070 --> 00:30:57,760
That day in the mansion,

682
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:01,160
I distantly heard you singing.

683
00:31:01,430 --> 00:31:04,160
There’s a part with high pitch.

684
00:31:05,190 --> 00:31:07,190
I forgot the lyrics.

685
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:10,680
After that part,

686
00:31:11,110 --> 00:31:12,920
I heard Fujin

687
00:31:13,560 --> 00:31:17,160
called His Majesty and Empress Zhen.

688
00:31:18,070 --> 00:31:19,800
When I came in to see her,

689
00:31:21,470 --> 00:31:22,950
she had passed away.

690
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:28,710
Fujin was loyal.

691
00:31:36,040 --> 00:31:37,310
Father, you’re here.

692
00:31:43,830 --> 00:31:44,640
I saw Fujin

693
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:47,680
not long ago.

694
00:31:50,760 --> 00:31:52,920
I never thought

695
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:56,070
we’d meet again like this.

696
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:57,590
You’re too kind.

697
00:32:00,230 --> 00:32:01,400
It’s unexpected.

698
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:07,950
You ever held me

699
00:32:07,950 --> 00:32:10,040
and took birds’ nest in this yard.

700
00:32:12,430 --> 00:32:14,190
It’s even more unexpected

701
00:32:14,590 --> 00:32:17,800
that you’re a commissioner now.

702
00:32:18,470 --> 00:32:19,520
Yet

703
00:32:21,040 --> 00:32:22,880
I became the last lord of Manchurians

704
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:26,400
who didn’t make it to be conferred.

705
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:28,590
Lord.

706
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:32,040
Times change. Dynasties transit.

707
00:32:34,230 --> 00:32:37,040
I will never forget

708
00:32:37,470 --> 00:32:39,110
the great kindness

709
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:42,560
of the late lord and Fujin.

710
00:32:45,110 --> 00:32:46,350
I felt a lot

711
00:32:48,190 --> 00:32:49,760
on this journey in Peking.

712
00:32:50,430 --> 00:32:51,430
Beijing

713
00:32:51,760 --> 00:32:53,430
changed into Peking.

714
00:32:55,430 --> 00:32:58,680
Back then my ancestors led Eight Banners

715
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:00,430
unified the country.

716
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:02,710
But unexpectedly,

717
00:33:04,350 --> 00:33:06,430
they were expelled back to hometown.

718
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:11,000
The emperor

719
00:33:11,350 --> 00:33:13,950
even stayed with the Japanese invaders.

720
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:15,760
What a shame.

721
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:17,950
Lord.

722
00:33:19,110 --> 00:33:22,640
Your patriotism is moving

723
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:24,400
and admirable.

724
00:33:26,470 --> 00:33:29,160
Times have changed.

725
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:32,560
Now Manchurian and Han

726
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:35,160
are all the countrymen of the Republic of China.

727
00:33:36,190 --> 00:33:36,830
In the future,

728
00:33:38,430 --> 00:33:40,110
we have to fight the enemy together

729
00:33:41,190 --> 00:33:42,760
and defend the country.

730
00:33:46,430 --> 00:33:47,160
Pull yourself together.

731
00:33:51,230 --> 00:33:52,040
Shang.

732
00:33:52,830 --> 00:33:54,950
The Tale of Dragon you performed last night

733
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,830
was excellent.

734
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:00,920
Everyone has the responsibility

735
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:04,040
to protect the country.

736
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:09,040
But the people don’t understand these nowadays.

737
00:34:10,760 --> 00:34:14,670
You should enlighten and influence them by your play.

738
00:34:16,389 --> 00:34:18,469
Father, I won’t let you down.

739
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:23,600
Shang.

740
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:27,560
When I

741
00:34:27,560 --> 00:34:29,360
first met you in Nanking,

742
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:33,710
I felt that your moves

743
00:34:33,710 --> 00:34:35,120
on the stage

744
00:34:37,120 --> 00:34:39,840
were quite like Ning Jiulang’s.

745
00:34:40,949 --> 00:34:42,389
Now I feel

746
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:45,120
your views are indeed

747
00:34:45,389 --> 00:34:47,469
like Jiulang’s.

748
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:48,469
Father.

749
00:34:48,870 --> 00:34:51,080
You compare me with Jiulang.

750
00:34:51,389 --> 00:34:52,909
I can’t afford it.

751
00:34:53,080 --> 00:34:53,909
No. No.

752
00:34:53,909 --> 00:34:56,150
Both you and Jiulang are ambitious.

753
00:34:56,710 --> 00:34:58,430
Back then Ning Jiulang

754
00:34:58,430 --> 00:34:59,800
wanted to modify operas,

755
00:35:00,950 --> 00:35:03,950
but he was too timid to do that.

756
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:08,080
He just slightly polished some operas.

757
00:35:08,190 --> 00:35:09,630
He didn’t creatively make operas

758
00:35:10,560 --> 00:35:12,800
until he met you.

759
00:35:12,870 --> 00:35:14,230
I remember, years ago,

760
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:18,280
Jiulang played emperor to support you.

761
00:35:18,630 --> 00:35:21,430
That Peking Opera

762
00:35:21,430 --> 00:35:22,870
was Iron Crown Diagram. Right?

763
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:25,800
It’s said the lyrics were well modified,

764
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:28,870
the moves and tone even better.

765
00:35:29,470 --> 00:35:31,390
Lord Qi was moved

766
00:35:32,080 --> 00:35:33,630
and cried.

767
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:35,870
The lyrics

768
00:35:35,870 --> 00:35:37,630
were modified by Mr. Du.

769
00:35:37,630 --> 00:35:38,670
Jiulang and I

770
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:40,630
composed the moves and the tone.

771
00:35:41,630 --> 00:35:42,390
Good.

772
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:46,040
It’s a pity that I had business in Nanking

773
00:35:46,630 --> 00:35:49,080
and missed it.

774
00:35:49,870 --> 00:35:52,000
Later, I heard that you went to Tianjin

775
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,360
to perform for the emperor.

776
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,760
Especially your line:

777
00:35:56,280 --> 00:36:00,390
I vow to bring justice to the monarch,

778
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:03,670
even if I would be smashed

779
00:36:04,470 --> 00:36:06,760
into pieces.

780
00:36:07,120 --> 00:36:08,760
It made the emperor cry.

781
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:13,390
I didn't know if the emperor cried or not.

782
00:36:13,950 --> 00:36:15,120
I don’t care about viewers

783
00:36:15,120 --> 00:36:16,910
when I perform.

784
00:36:17,950 --> 00:36:18,950
Viewer?

785
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:25,000
Performing for the emperor

786
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,630
is a great honor.

787
00:36:30,040 --> 00:36:31,630
You call emperor Xuantong

788
00:36:31,630 --> 00:36:33,870
one of your viewers?

789
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:37,230
You are bragging.

790
00:36:40,600 --> 00:36:44,120
But I like your stubbornness.

791
00:36:46,430 --> 00:36:48,040
Is the opera still on show?

792
00:36:49,560 --> 00:36:51,320
Since Jiulang retired,

793
00:36:51,950 --> 00:36:53,470
Iron Crown Diagram has been hung up.

794
00:36:53,470 --> 00:36:54,190
Why?

795
00:36:57,390 --> 00:36:59,120
No one can play Emperor Chongzhen

796
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:02,630
as well as Jiulang does.

797
00:37:05,840 --> 00:37:06,800
What a pity.

798
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:09,840
What a pity.

799
00:37:10,470 --> 00:37:11,360
Then

800
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:13,000
my godfather repeated that

801
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:16,190
it’s a pity he didn't watch Jiulang’s performance.

802
00:37:16,710 --> 00:37:18,710
He also asked me a lot about Jiulang.

803
00:37:20,390 --> 00:37:22,280
Did he miss Jiulang so much?

804
00:37:22,710 --> 00:37:24,280
Not only him.

805
00:37:24,470 --> 00:37:25,630
I missed him too.

806
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,120
It’s been a long time since we met.

807
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:30,120
I’m dying to perform

808
00:37:30,600 --> 00:37:31,600
with him again.

809
00:37:35,630 --> 00:37:37,630
How can I let you die

810
00:37:37,630 --> 00:37:39,840
for this?

811
00:37:41,080 --> 00:37:42,430
I have an idea.

812
00:37:42,430 --> 00:37:44,360
Cheng, what do you mean?

813
00:37:45,390 --> 00:37:48,080
Liu Hanyun will return to Nanking to report
at the end of this month.

814
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:50,870
Commander Cao asked me to arrange banquet for him.

815
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:54,630
If you really want to see Ning Jiulang,

816
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:56,630
you may invite Jiulang

817
00:37:56,630 --> 00:37:59,040
to perform with you in his name.

818
00:37:59,230 --> 00:38:00,630
Will it work?

819
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:02,910
I don’t know Jiulang’s temper.

820
00:38:02,910 --> 00:38:04,040
I am not sure,

821
00:38:04,230 --> 00:38:05,520
but you can have a try.

822
00:38:05,520 --> 00:38:07,520
That’s a must, Mr. Cheng.

823
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:09,280
Got it, Mr. Shang.

824
00:38:09,390 --> 00:38:11,630
I’m going back to draw up an invitation.

825
00:38:12,800 --> 00:38:13,560
Leader.

826
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:14,910
Sixi’er drove out the doctor

827
00:38:14,910 --> 00:38:16,230
you invited for Zhouzi.

828
00:38:16,430 --> 00:38:17,520
He didn’t allow him to treat Zhouzi.

829
00:38:17,520 --> 00:38:19,120
Zhouzi hit the wall hard.

830
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:20,950
He can’t die. I’m going to see him.

831
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:22,600
Sixi’er won’t let you in.

832
00:38:22,600 --> 00:38:24,150
Don’t fight with them.

833
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:27,710
Your leader has never

834
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,280
cared about someone so much.

835
00:38:30,040 --> 00:38:31,520
Zhouzi is lucky.

836
00:38:31,520 --> 00:38:32,280
Right.

837
00:39:03,040 --> 00:39:05,080
Don't move. Lie down.

838
00:39:13,470 --> 00:39:14,630
Sixi’er

839
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,630
didn’t let me in.

840
00:39:17,630 --> 00:39:19,280
So, I went over the wall to see you.

841
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:38,950
Is Sixi’er a human?

842
00:39:39,630 --> 00:39:41,630
How come he left you even without water?

843
00:39:47,910 --> 00:39:49,360
He has always treated me harshly.

844
00:39:50,080 --> 00:39:51,120
He doesn’t let me perform.

845
00:39:54,670 --> 00:39:56,230
Thanks to Mr. Shang,

846
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,630
I performed finally.

847
00:40:00,520 --> 00:40:02,000
But he hates my guts now.

848
00:40:03,080 --> 00:40:04,230
Mr. Shang.

849
00:40:04,870 --> 00:40:07,120
I may die here.

850
00:40:08,600 --> 00:40:09,360
I see you

851
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:11,520
before I die.

852
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:13,840
I...

853
00:40:16,190 --> 00:40:17,760
I don't have any regret.

854
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:19,000
Zhouzi.

855
00:40:19,870 --> 00:40:21,320
Cheer up.

856
00:40:21,630 --> 00:40:22,390
You

857
00:40:22,390 --> 00:40:24,560
are a genius performer.

858
00:40:24,840 --> 00:40:27,520
Don’t die in Sixi’er’s hands.

859
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:32,120
Zhouzi. Zhouzi.

860
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:35,840
I try so hard to teach you and save you.

861
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:37,320
You know why?

862
00:40:38,230 --> 00:40:39,630
I want to take you as my apprentice.

863
00:40:40,150 --> 00:40:42,470
I will pass all my teachings to you.

864
00:40:42,870 --> 00:40:46,560
Zhouzi. Zhouzi.

865
00:40:58,000 --> 00:41:00,120
The doorman has gone inside long

866
00:41:00,600 --> 00:41:02,280
and didn’t reply us.

867
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:03,360
Mr. Cheng.

868
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,120
Jiulang still doesn’t want

869
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:06,470
to see me, does he?

870
00:41:08,040 --> 00:41:09,600
It’s in vain.

871
00:41:09,600 --> 00:41:10,950
Let’s go home.

872
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:16,950
Mr. Shang.

873
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,120
I haven’t asked you.

874
00:41:19,950 --> 00:41:21,910
Since Ning Jiulang taught you operas

875
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:23,470
and you admire him so much,

876
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:25,280
how come he’s reluctant

877
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:26,230
to see you now?

878
00:41:28,080 --> 00:41:29,560
Jiulang is no ordinary man.

879
00:41:30,120 --> 00:41:31,840
How could I know what he thinks?

880
00:41:32,630 --> 00:41:34,950
You probably offended him.

881
00:41:34,950 --> 00:41:35,760
I didn’t.

882
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:36,910
I got along well with him.

883
00:41:38,080 --> 00:41:39,280
One day,

884
00:41:39,760 --> 00:41:42,320
he prepared many dishes to treat me.

885
00:41:42,870 --> 00:41:43,910
I ate all up.

886
00:41:43,910 --> 00:41:46,120
Then he said he had nothing to teach me anymore

887
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:47,360
and drove me away.

888
00:41:52,560 --> 00:41:53,760
He is your master,

889
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:55,800
and you should prepare dishes for him.

890
00:41:55,800 --> 00:41:57,040
Look at you.

891
00:41:57,520 --> 00:41:59,430
Your master prepared dishes for you.

892
00:42:00,630 --> 00:42:02,080
Shame on you. You have no manners.

893
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:04,470
If I were Ning Jiulang, I would also drive you away.

894
00:42:09,430 --> 00:42:11,630
Mr. Shang. Mr. Cheng. Please follow me.

895
00:42:19,470 --> 00:42:20,120
Please.

896
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:28,560
The people in Peking said

897
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:31,150
Lord Qi is the richest among the elders.

898
00:42:31,390 --> 00:42:32,910
It lives up to the name.

899
00:42:35,630 --> 00:42:36,390
Cheng.

900
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:38,430
I’m wondering.

901
00:42:38,870 --> 00:42:40,430
The emperor has run away.

902
00:42:41,040 --> 00:42:42,870
How come the princes and royal descendants

903
00:42:43,120 --> 00:42:44,840
are still so rich?

904
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:46,870
The antiques and the land

905
00:42:47,150 --> 00:42:48,800
left by their ancestors

906
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:50,670
are enough for them to live on.

907
00:42:51,560 --> 00:42:53,670
Besides, Lord Qi is far-sighted.

908
00:42:53,950 --> 00:42:56,280
He set up industries in the concession long ago.

909
00:42:56,630 --> 00:42:58,520
Even the emperor spoke highly of him

910
00:42:59,080 --> 00:43:01,520
and meant to invite him

911
00:43:01,710 --> 00:43:03,230
to be the Minister of Industry.

912
00:43:03,870 --> 00:43:05,390
Didn’t he agree?

913
00:43:06,230 --> 00:43:07,080
Well,

914
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:11,630
I don’t know.

915
00:43:12,630 --> 00:43:13,800
Maybe he’s old

916
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:14,950
and didn’t want to leave homeland.

917
00:43:15,910 --> 00:43:17,910
When you left Pingyang,

918
00:43:18,520 --> 00:43:19,950
weren’t you upset?

919
00:43:20,040 --> 00:43:21,120
No, I wasn't.

920
00:43:21,520 --> 00:43:22,670
I was happy.

921
00:43:23,320 --> 00:43:25,150
My father told me about Peking, the Forbidden City

922
00:43:25,320 --> 00:43:27,520
and the like when I was young.

923
00:43:27,630 --> 00:43:29,630
So, I expected to perform in Peking

924
00:43:29,760 --> 00:43:31,000
when I grew up.

925
00:43:31,630 --> 00:43:32,840
People move up the ladder.

926
00:43:33,560 --> 00:43:35,320
I was very happy when I left Pingyang.

927
00:43:40,040 --> 00:43:41,390
You are no ordinary man as well.
